Package unitControlModule.stateFactories.actions.executableActions.steering

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SteeringOperation
    SteeringOperation.java --- Interface for all SteeringOperations the Unit can use to change various Vectors.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseSteeringOperation
    BaseSteeringOperation.java --- Most basic steering action.
    SteeringFactory
    SteeringFactory.java --- Factory for generating the final version of a steering Vector.
    SteeringOperationChokePoints
    SteeringOperationChokePoints.java --- SteeringOperation which targets ChokePoints on the map.
    SteeringOperationEnemiesInConfidenceRange
    SteeringOperationEnemiesInConfidenceRange.java --- SteeringOperation which targets enemies that are near the Unit and inside its confidence range.
    SteeringOperationSpecificUnit
    SteeringOperationSpecificUnit.java --- SteeringOperation which targets a specific Unit on the map.
    SteeringOperationStartingLocation
    SteeringOperationStartingLocation.java --- SteeringOperation which targets the Player's starting location.
    SteeringOperationStrongestPlayerArea
    SteeringOperationStrongestPlayerArea.java --- SteeringOperation which targets the area with the highest Player strength on the map based on the tracker's information.
